title: Picky Market Express
description: This shop carries raw organic superfoods (fresh spirulina paste, cacao, hemp seeds, cacao, maca, carob, chia seeds), vegan protein powders, organic gluten free baking mixes. Located between Asoke BTS & Sukumvit MRT station. 2014 reported relocated from Interchange 21 Building, 399 Sukumvit, Klongtoey-Nua, Wattana.
